 Just several steps, this Chinese old man can make a "golden butterfly" with a Ginkgo leaf. As a master of straw plaiting, he can turn leaves of different kinds into vivid animals in a minute. He is now a well-known handcrafts man on Kuaishou, a video platform similar to TikTok. Video credit to "Grandpa's handcrafts" (kuaishou#ymb11950), posted on Chinese online video-sharing platform Kuaishou.  (Source: Kuaishou) 